---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Parker Mutsuz — developer, filmmaker, and photographer.">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center min-h-[calc(100dvh-10rem)]">

    <!-- Tertiary -->
    <p class="font-mono text-[13px] tracking-[0.08em] uppercase text-[#999999] dark:text-[#666666] mb-5">
      About
    </p>

    <!-- Primary -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-black dark:text-white">
      Parker Mutsuz
    </h1>

    <!-- Secondary: bio -->
    <div class="mt-8 md:mt-12 max-w-prose space-y-5">
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-[#e8e8e8]">
        I'm a developer, filmmaker, and photographer working at the edges of code and image.
        My work spans software products, short documentary films, and long-form photography — each discipline
        informing the others in ways I'm still figuring out.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-[#e8e8e8]">
        On the software side, I build tools that prioritise clarity and directness — products where the
        interface gets out of the way and lets people do the thing they came to do. On film, I'm drawn to
        quiet subjects: makers, craft, the unglamorous hours before the interesting part happens.
        Photography is where I slow down; a single image has to carry everything a video gets to distribute
        across time.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-[#e8e8e8]">
        This site is a single place for all of it — writing, projects, films, and photos — without one
        practice being subordinated to another.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Tertiary: contact -->
    <p class="mt-10 md:mt-12">
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@selambuarada.com"
        class="font-mono text-[13px] tracking-[0.08em] uppercase text-[#999999] dark:text-[#666666] hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors underline underline-offset-4"
      >
        hello@selambuarada.com
      </a>
    </p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
